<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #B57919;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .cta {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            background-color: #B57919;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password associated with your account. Please use the verification
                code below to proceed:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #B57919; font-size: 24px;">{{code}}</strong>
            </div>
            <p>If you didnâ€™t request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team if you have
                any concerns.</p>
            <p>You can reset your password by clicking the button below:</p>
            <a href="{{url}}" class="cta">Reset Your Password</a>
            <p>For security reasons, this code will expire shortly. Make sure to complete the process soon!</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p>Vitaluxe Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Vitaluxe. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>